Action 5 : Déploiement et Exécution du Flux Kestra
Ouvre Kestra sur http://localhost:8089.
Crée un nouveau Flow et colle le code YAML de la Step 1 (celui qui fait le mc mb pour créer le bucket, lance docker-compose-ingestion.yml, puis docker-compose-generator.yml en mode live, et valide les fichiers).
Clique sur "Execute". Kestra va maintenant lancer ton code Spark stream_to_minio.py

Flow p12_step1_complet : 
fait le mc mb pour créer le bucket, 
lance docker-compose-ingestion.yml, 
puis docker-compose-generator.yml en mode live, 
et valide les fichiers

id: p12_step1_complet
namespace: poc.didier

tasks:
  - id: setup_minio_bucket
    type: io.kestra.plugin.scripts.shell.Commands
    containerImage: minio/mc
    taskRunner:
      type: io.kestra.plugin.scripts.runner.docker.Docker
      networkMode: poc_network
    env:
      MC_HOST_minio: "http://admin:password@minio:9000"
    commands:
      - mc mb --ignore-existing minio/raw

  - id: start_infra_ingestion
    type: io.kestra.plugin.scripts.shell.Commands
    containerImage: docker:cli
    taskRunner:
      type: io.kestra.plugin.scripts.runner.docker.Docker
      networkMode: poc_network
      volumes:
        - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock
    commands:
      - |
        cat <<EOF > docker-compose-all.yml
        services:
          redpanda:
            image: docker.redpanda.com/redpandadata/redpanda:latest
            container_name: redpanda
            networks: [poc_network]
            command: >
              redpanda start --smp 1 --memory 1G --overprovisioned --node-id 0 --check=false 
              --kafka-addr internal://0.0.0.0:9092,external://0.0.0.0:19092 
              --advertise-kafka-addr internal://redpanda:9092,external://localhost:19092 
              --schema-registry-addr internal://0.0.0.0:8081
          
          redpanda-console:
            image: docker.redpanda.com/redpandadata/console:latest
            container_name: redpanda_console
            networks: [poc_network]
            environment:
              - KAFKA_BROKERS=redpanda:9092
              - KAFKA_SCHEMAREGISTRY_URLS=http://redpanda:8081
            ports: ["8081:8080"]

          spark-streaming:
            image: poc-spark-streaming:latest
            container_name: spark_streaming_ingestion
            networks: [poc_network]
            environment:
              - MINIO_ENDPOINT=http://minio:9000
              - MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=admin
              - MINIO_SECRET_KEY=password
              - REDPANDA_BROKERS=redpanda:9092
            volumes:
              - /home/dev/projects/p12/poc/spark/jobs:/opt/spark/jobs
              - /home/dev/projects/p12/poc/spark/libs:/opt/spark/libs
              - /home/dev/projects/p12/poc/generator/schemas:/opt/spark/schemas
              - /home/dev/projects/p12/poc/spark/checkpoints:/opt/spark/checkpoints
            command: >
              /opt/spark/bin/spark-submit 
              --master local[*] 
              --packages org.apache.spark:spark-avro_2.12:3.5.0
              --jars /opt/spark/libs/*.jar
              /opt/spark/jobs/stream_to_minio.py

          generator-live:
            image: poc-generator-live:latest
            container_name: generator_live
            networks: [poc_network]
            restart: always
            environment:
              - GEN_MODE=LIVE
              - REDPANDA_BROKERS=redpanda:9092
              - SCHEMA_REGISTRY_URL=http://redpanda:8081

        networks:
          poc_network:
            external: true
        EOF
      - docker compose -f docker-compose-all.yml down --remove-orphans
      - docker compose -f docker-compose-all.yml up -d
      - sleep 15
      - docker exec redpanda rpk topic create cdc.public.salaries || true
      - echo "Ingestion en cours... attente de 120s"
      - sleep 120
      - echo "Nettoyage automatique de la stack..."
      - docker compose -f docker-compose-all.yml down # <--- Ajout du nettoyage automatique

  - id: validate_parquet_files
    type: io.kestra.plugin.scripts.shell.Commands
    containerImage: minio/mc
    taskRunner:
      type: io.kestra.plugin.scripts.runner.docker.Docker
      networkMode: poc_network
    env:
      MC_HOST_minio: "http://admin:password@minio:9000"
    commands:
      - "echo 'Liste des fichiers trouvés :'"
      - mc ls -r minio/raw/rh/salaries/
      - |
        COUNT=$(mc ls -r minio/raw/rh/salaries/ | wc -l)
        if [ "$COUNT" -gt 0 ]; then
          echo "SUCCÈS : $COUNT fichiers détectés."
        else
          echo "ERREUR : Aucun fichier trouvé."
          exit 1
        fi